" /> <br />\n<br />\n到而家一份文件check 5-6 次先敢出街，但每次sd之前都好大壓力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我對人present個d 就好smooth，轉數尚算ok，都唔明點解自己有時一做文件野成個白痴咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4536a60dfde0a95f78e03f2048b40ae4e5f78f2f","tid":2048593,"uid":98229,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T14:32:56.000Z","msg":"屌以為自己開po<br />\n每次有文件都好認真check咗廿萬次搞咗成粒鐘先出到<br />\n到最後每次都搵唔到問題先俾老細<br />\n然後每次老細都會搵到實際存在嘅問題<br />\n我自己聽老細講完之後又發現嗰啲真係唔應該錯<br />\n跟著佢問我點解會錯<br />\n我真係答唔出<br />\n<br />\n有時覺得根本自己能力不足"},{"pid":"51e4cb10c0cdff64f691a889a119f4151f10cd83","tid":2048593,"uid":105192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"167d8553900b564be408abab7828125ac2162277","tid":2048593,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e8a1e415ed2f44e8d831dfc070b888fa2a43ef6e","tid":2048593,"uid":105192,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:37:55.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前讀書嗰陣從來都唔發現 成績仲唔錯 出到黎先發現自己成日甩甩漏漏比人感覺好似好蠢咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"手足以前讀咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀書嗰時做數都成日甩漏大意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:02:53.000Z","msg":"當年好好彩入到三大 真係出到黎先覺得自己有問題<br />\n成日有typo都見唔到照出街 明明check左好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b86d1d93304eaf57c5f2da84c6b4fac6ec0b736","tid":2048593,"uid":196266,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a0210d25d086ab474b37fd69d39af06430040991","tid":2048593,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"109c593ac8c2dd5b71ea72df84b81939ab8c71e2","tid":2048593,"uid":264362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"應該都係ADHD，我keep住有呢個問題不過冇check,返工係咁錯careless mistake,十幾年黎都係咁，check十次都會有錯，樓上個d正常人唔會理解"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\